  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096050/extras/46ce938e4b3c0cf4e970399df5c958e9.avif?t=1759090165\" width=600 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096050/extras/29dcc79f7dafa2c9fb8ecdbe9d1a78d1.avif?t=1759090165\" width=615 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096050/extras/f47b1894c263c2591a46e4874ff090be.webp?t=1759090165\" width=615 height=60 /></span>Mark had a terrible car accident. His wife Jane, who was sitting in the passenger seat, died in the accident. Overwhelmed with guilt, Mark moves to the old country house they had bought to enjoy the summers and starts organizing his wife's funeral. But the house soon reveals a disturbing presence: Jane's.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mark is followed by a psychologist who has left some recordings in the house. In these, the psychologist claims to have planted puzzles to keep Mark's mind occupied and help him process the grief, freeing himself from guilt.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096050/extras/2d89eed9d0d4e69ec068da8ef6b71361.webp?t=1759090165\" width=615 height=60 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Challenging Puzzles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096050/extras/592fd5c76eaa87455896e0f23b9aafd0.avif?t=1759090165\" width=614 height=300 /></span>Solve intricate puzzles that will test your logic and intuition.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Mental Health</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096050/extras/8a6a247f3c607f8accf761278eb6dd9c.avif?t=1759090165\" width=614 height=300 /></span>Whenever Mark experiences paranormal phenomena, his level of anxiety increases. Find rosaries and pray near crucifixes to lower the anxiety level and restore mental health.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Deer Woman</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096050/extras/51d55aa1854fff5ad59006cd954dc07d.avif?t=1759090165\" width=614 height=300 /></span>Hide wherever you can to escape the spirit chasing Mark.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Soundtrack</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096050/extras/2a851872488b1f40b8e63fa125a0f235.avif?t=1759090165\" width=614 height=300 /></span>An eerie soundtrack that amplifies the horror experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Setting</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096050/extras/079341f8068f4d17840199414d50b126.avif?t=1759090165\" width=614 height=300 /></span>Explore the country house full of dark corners and spooky surprises.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Jumpscare</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096050/extras/e5f2446653c20818316fd9b39d8a75de.avif?t=1759090165\" width=614 height=300 /></span>Prepare for a terrifying experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096050/extras/00c3018c7785638cd881ba334d934885.avif?t=1759090165\" width=614 height=300 /></span>A plot that will keep you glued to the screen and leave you speechless.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Recordings</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096050/extras/4d593590a2dfc3c6ce867dddf9e16783.avif?t=1759090165\" width=614 height=300 /></span>Listen to the psychologist's recordings at any time to discover clues and deepen the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Graphics</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096050/extras/b5596a37268604cad8cb456f9c442ec5.avif?t=1759090165\" width=614 height=300 /></span>Detailed environments and characters that make the experience even more immersive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Anxiety</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096050/extras/9669f98b0a219e688d191c012d43f27f.avif?t=1759090165\" width=614 height=300 /></span>Experience a continuous tension that will keep you on the edge of your seat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096050/extras/70aaafcd7936b07d7649cb9fd027683d.webp?t=1759090165\" width=615 height=60 /></span>Scary Shadow Spot is a series of horror games that pays homage to the classic TV show The Twilight Zone. Each chapter features a unique and chilling story.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096050/extras/46ce938e4b3c0cf4e970399df5c958e9.avif?t=1759090165\" width=600 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096050/extras/29dcc79f7dafa2c9fb8ecdbe9d1a78d1.avif?t=1759090165\" width=615 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096050/extras/f47b1894c263c2591a46e4874ff090be.webp?t=1759090165\" width=615 height=60 /></span>Mark had a terrible car accident. His wife Jane, who was sitting in the passenger seat, died in the accident. Overwhelmed with guilt, Mark moves to the old country house they had bought to enjoy the summers and starts organizing his wife's funeral. But the house soon reveals a disturbing presence: Jane's.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mark is followed by a psychologist who has left some recordings in the house. In these, the psychologist claims to have planted puzzles to keep Mark's mind occupied and help him process the grief, freeing himself from guilt.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096050/extras/2d89eed9d0d4e69ec068da8ef6b71361.webp?t=1759090165\" width=615 height=60 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Challenging Puzzles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096050/extras/592fd5c76eaa87455896e0f23b9aafd0.avif?t=1759090165\" width=614 height=300 /></span>Solve intricate puzzles that will test your logic and intuition.</p><p clas